room_title: Escape room "Capone" by Trapped Escape Game in Pigeon Forge
review: Have done the Capone Room and Alcatraz. Both were awesome and extremely challenging. The staff was awesome and extremely friendly. Will probably go again tonight!

room_title: Escape room "Capone" by Trapped Escape Game in Pigeon Forge
review: Me, my wife, and my brother went to the Haunted Cabin and the Capone rooms two days in a row! We loved it and the staff,especially Jae, was super nice and friendly! We are definitely going back! This is our favorite escape game place so far!
